dcterms:description: A dataset containing 2,075,259 data points of household voltage measurements at one-minute intervals. It is highly volatile but normally distributed, following a seasonal pattern each year.
dcterms:title: Voltage Dataset

dcterms:creator: T. Lin
T. Guo
K. Aberer
dcterms:description: A resampled dataset of size 41,786 at a frequency of 1Hz, containing methane concentration measurements. It is skewed to the right of its mean value and exhibits sharp changes with medium to low volatility.
dcterms:title: Methane Dataset

dcterms:creator: T. Lin
T. Guo
K. Aberer
dcterms:description: A dataset containing 13,563 data points of the composite New York Stock Exchange (NYSE) closing prices from 31-12-1965 to 15-11-2019. It exhibits low volatility initially, becoming more volatile after the year 2000.
dcterms:title: NYSE Dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 3,094 data points of the composite Johannesburg Stock Exchange (JSE) closing prices from 2007-09-18 to 2019-12-31. It is less volatile compared to the NYSE and shows a symmetrical distribution around its mean value.
dcterms:title: JSE Dataset
